{"tid":1298720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉：不支持政府大可脫離建制　田北辰：不知所謂","createTime":"2019-07-09T02:32:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T16:12:10.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1082,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"70525f8c1871c1e9d5931af7d2f7d14686f0503f","tid":1298720,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190709/s00001/4c5efb63feb7eaa8f5fdb7f19bde4047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190709%2Fs00001%2F4c5efb63feb7eaa8f5fdb7f19bde4047.jpg&h=ca19d123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新民黨主席葉劉淑儀昨日（8日）在記者會上表示，若實政圓桌立法會議員田北辰等人認為不應支持政府，大可公開脫離建制派，以至辭去港區人大職位。田北辰今晨（9日）接受港台節目訪問時，就批評有關說法「不知所謂」。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰稱，人大目的是為了監察中央政府，而自己擔任人大期間曾就不同議題發聲，例如銅鑼灣書店事件等，故認為自己並無失職。他又認為身為立法會議員，職責在於監察政府，而非配合政府。<br />\n<br />\n他反駁葉劉淑儀稱行會等同「執政聯盟」的說法，稱所謂「執政聯盟」只是好聽些的字眼，其實也等同幫政府「箍票」。他重申，行會成員不應有政黨背景，並要由政治中立的人擔任，「這些人可以和中央友好，但也不要太唯命是從」。"},{"pid":"5c97b590a2f5b9cf7c8af3ab9d91424ea83fac0b","tid":1298720,"uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:32:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190709/s00001/1562637435960/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190709%2Fs00001%2F1562637435960%2F&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0do6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=0fae2210\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190709%2Fs00001%2F1562637435960%2F&h=c2b8889c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190709/s00001/1562637435960/</a>"},{"pid":"cb4415e47f1cf14081e231d232fe64353047f3b2","tid":1298720,"uid":126436,"like":176,"dislike":0,"score":176,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:33:06.000Z","msg":"講人話"},{"pid":"5c90deea4ae710855309aa5a5f189880a39a4ccd","tid":1298720,"uid":43133,"like":422,"dislike":1,"score":